    "description": "快叫上好友（或者结识新友！），一起在《节日大作战》中尽情狂欢吧！这是一款热闹非凡的多人大逃杀游戏，拥有各种奇葩武器和令人捧腹的场景，保准让你笑得前仰后合。闪电、大鱼、喷火器…… 各种脑洞大开的武器等你来发现！最多8人同场竞技，每一局都是刺激的生存挑战！快来加入这场疯狂派对，和好友们一起嗨翻天！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282650/extras/d24e36f2bf213d68253aa483faef79ca.poster.avif?t=1739519252\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282650/extras/d24e36f2bf213d68253aa483faef79ca.webm?t=1739519252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282650/extras/d24e36f2bf213d68253aa483faef79ca.mp4?t=1739519252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>神奇的武器装备</strong><br>各种奇葩装备，保证每局比赛都让你笑到肚子疼！用喷火器把对手烤成灰烬，用摇滚吉他撕裂敌人，或者用弹弓发射保龄球将他们击倒！挥动巨型鱼猛击对手，用电蚊拍狠狠电他们，或者用黏糊糊的青蛙舌头将他们卷走。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282650/extras/8d0e2b1a14718fad2cad8ba47117636f.poster.avif?t=1739519252\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282650/extras/8d0e2b1a14718fad2cad8ba47117636f.webm?t=1739519252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282650/extras/8d0e2b1a14718fad2cad8ba47117636f.mp4?t=1739519252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>节日吉祥物开趴!</strong><br>南瓜杰克、复活节兔子、丘比特、年兽、狐仙、悟空……... 全球节日吉祥物大集合，等你来认领！看他们战场上各显神通，花式炫技！为你心仪的角色换上各种炫酷服装，做好战斗准备吧！。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282650/extras/00d50aa18f9e38d05510cdcb1c30b7e3.poster.avif?t=1739519252\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282650/extras/00d50aa18f9e38d05510cdcb1c30b7e3.webm?t=1739519252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282650/extras/00d50aa18f9e38d05510cdcb1c30b7e3.mp4?t=1739519252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>多样模式，快乐翻倍！</strong><br>除了激烈的战斗，《节日大作战》还准备了超多考验脑力、策略和技巧的小游戏。不管是躲避障碍、智胜对手，还是运用各种奇葩武器，丰富多样的游戏内容，让你和朋友们玩到停不下来！<br><br>游戏特色<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>派对狂欢: </strong>最多支持8人同场竞技，一起加入这场刺激、快节奏的战斗。<br></li><li><strong>海量武器: </strong>脑洞大开武器库，从抓钩到喷火器，统统等你来发掘！<br></li><li><strong>自定义角色: </strong>给你的吉祥物穿上各式盛装，打造最闪亮的派对明星！<br></li><li><strong>多样挑战: </strong>参与各种独具特色的迷你游戏。<br></li><li><strong>鱼拍乐趣:</strong> 用鱼拍人——啪！啪！啪！ </li></ul><br>《节日大作战》欢乐派对，邀你一起笑翻天！ 每一场战斗都是盛大的节日庆典！",
